"*** PING\n"
" - test whether a particular host is reachable\n"
"*FORMAT: ping -i <eth_name> [-c <count>] -d <destination>\n"
"\t <eth_name>   - name of network interface.\n"
"\t <count>      - number of packets.\n"
"\t              by default: 4\n"
"\t <destination>- ip address of host.\n"
